Program: Thinking Allowed
Title: Intoxication
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01pg54j
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 31 Dec 2012
Intoxication - In a special programme, Laurie Taylor explores the role and meaning of both alcohol and drugs in human life. Why do so many people chose to alter their consciousness with stimulants, whether legal or illicit? Professor James Mills, the author of 'Cannabis Nation..' is joined by Professor Fiona Measham and Professor Chris Hackley. Producer: Jayne Egerton. Show less